{
  "stem": "8527.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I pictured myself that I was going to be someplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was dressed in a shirt and tie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was on the third floor in an office someplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I saw myself as an adult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think things like that kept you going, because you had to have some kind of hope.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once in a while she would come in and tell us the bad news that the Russians were being defeated, that the Germans were advancing, and so on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's basically the way life went on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Towards the end.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would be by myself in the attic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Towards the end, she was-- she came in, spent some time in the attic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I-- see, I wasn't part of the deal as far as being hidden, so there's nothing she could do for me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was afraid to antagonize them, OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But anyway, my mother, as I said, was in hiding with this man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And about four or five months before the-- before we got freed, before the Russians came in, she came in to tell us that my mother was just brought into town on a wagon, tied to a wagon, and the-- to the German police, and she was shot.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my mother and that guy survived in hiding for about a year, year and a half.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they finally were turned in by this Pole.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In fact, my niece started writing to Poland to get the court documents because after the war, those people were taken to-- that Polack, Dzujemblo was his name, was taken to court.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was sentenced to five year in prison.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
